---
// Slim announcement banner between Hero and About
---

<section class="bg-[#f3ecf8] border-y border-[#ddd0ed]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-[#a180be] mb-2">2026 Conference</p>
    <h2 class="font-['Open_Sauce_Sans'] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#3d2466] mb-3">
      Registration is open for GirlCon 2026!
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[#7c6f8a] max-w-lg mx-auto mb-5">
      GirlCon Virtual runs <strong class="text-[#6b4fa0]">June 25–26</strong> online, and GirlCon Chicago is <strong class="text-[#6b4fa0]">June 27</strong> in-person at RSM Chicago.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
      <a
        href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/girlcon-2026-tickets-1989781007557"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3 rounded-full bg-[#6b4fa0] text-white font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#5a3f8a] transition-colors"
      >
        Register for GirlCon Chicago →
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/girlcon-2026-virtual-tickets-1990421786143"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3 rounded-full border-2 border-[#6b4fa0] text-[#6b4fa0] font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#6b4fa0] hover:text-white transition-colors"
      >
        Register for GirlCon Virtual →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
